                        </persName> towards the west, and the land late of <persName>
                           <forename>Simon</forename> de <surname>Morkote</surname>
                        </persName> towards the east. <gap/> Given at <placeName role="date" key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                        </placeName>. 
